com.stormpath.sdk.phone

Interface Phone

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Auditable, Deletable, Resource, Saveable

    public interface Phone
extends Resource, Saveable, Deletable, Auditable
    A phone is associated with an Account to be used for Multi Factor Authentication.
